

#Azure AD connect sync 
  Start-ADSyncSyncCycle -PolicyType Initial (initiates a full
  synchronization)
  Start-ADSyncSyncCycle -PolicyType Delta (initiates a delta
  synchronization)


#CHECK DC Forest functional level
get-ADForest

AZURE AD CONNECT
  Cannot be installed on Server Core (must have the GUI version)
for password synchronization, you must run on Server 2008 R2 SP1 or later
if using AD Connect with ADFS, you must run on Server 2012 R2 or later
if global administrator has MFA, you must configure a trusted URL https://secure.aadcdn.microsoftonline-p.com
Server must be a member of a domain and connect to a writable DC. Synchronization occurs on
     !!!!PORTS!!!!
    DNS TCP/UDP 53
    Kerberos TCP/UDP 88
    RPC TCP 135
    LDAP TCP/UDP 389
    SSL TCP 443
    SMB TCP 445

